Hi Greg,

What you need is a "butt tent". They hang off the rear hatch and extend 
the rear cargo area to be big enough to sleep on. Then you sleep one kid 
across the back seat and another in a cot across the front seats. 
Problem solved and no pop-top required.

http://www.kookymathteacher.com/rearender/rearendtent.html

Happy Trails,

